{
  "texts": [
    "\"Oh, Jonah,\" they entreated him.",
    "\"Prophet of the Most High, have you come to tell us again of our impending doom?\"",
    "With a heavy heart, Jonah recounted the message given to him by God.",
    "\"Forty days more, and Nineveh shall be overthrown!\" he declared.",
    "Yet, this time, he spoke without conviction."
  ]
}